  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Railguns, Area-of-Effect and Figh=
ters</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DGramE>The <span class=3DSpellE>Zakkal<=
/span></span>
  are a species shrouded in controversy.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>During the darkest times in the ancient galaxy, when=
 war
  losses to the <span class=3DSpellE>Shakturi</span> were enormous, the Hum=
ans
  were desperate to replenish their ranks. They covertly attempted to splic=
e <span
  class=3DSpellE>Securan</span> DNA into unsuspecting participants to take
  advantage of the <span class=3DSpellE>Securans</span> genetic propensity =
for
  reproduction.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The results were somewhat successful, producing an
  intelligent and fertile species. But the new hybrids were genetically
  unstable, prone to certain diseases and developmental challenges.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>When this became known to the <span class=3DSpellE>S=
ecuran</span>
  State, the Human/<span class=3DSpellE>Securan</span> alliance was almost
  shattered beyond repair.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Securans</span> demanded the
  destruction of the hybrids, but the Humans resisted. A deal was struck wh=
ere
  the few thousand hybrids were sent to the far reaches of the Galaxy. They
  were transplanted to an obscure desert planet near the edge of the galaxy=
 in
  the hopes they would survive the ongoing <span class=3DSpellE>Shakturi</s=
pan>
  conflict.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The hybrids (later calling themselves <span class=3D=
SpellE>Zakkal</span>)
  adapted to the harsh climate through sheer ingenuity and reproductive
  capacity. As their civilization re-entered space, contact with scattered
  remnants of other races began.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DGramE>The <span class=3DSpellE>Zakkal<=
/span></span>
  are naturally friendly to other races even though they have every right n=
ot
  to be. They are fatalists, seeing their history as the intended will of s=
ome
  larger force. They hold no ill will towards Humans or <span class=3DSpell=
E>Securans</span>,
  though those factions are less amenable.</p>
